{{one source|date=May 2017}}

The following list shows a compact version of the colors in the List of colors [[List of colors: A–F|A–F]], [[List of colors: G–M|G–M]], and [[List of colors: N–Z|N–Z]] articles. The list shows the color and its name. Hovering over the color box shows the [[HSV color space|HSV]], [[RGB]], and [[Hex triplet|#hex]] values for the color in the tool tip.

There are 11 main colors. The main 11 colors are red, orange, yellow, green, blue, purple, pink, brown, gray, black and white.<ref>{{cite web |title=What are Basic Color Names |url=https://thelandofcolor.com/11-basic-color-names/ |website=the land of color}}</ref> The rest of the colors on this list are just different types, combinations and shades of the main 11 colors.

